<item>
            <title>[LU-11068] &quot;not a valid identifier&quot; in lbuild caused by an extra space</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11068</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When using lbuild to build, got following error:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Downloading kernel SRPM&lt;br/&gt;
./lbuild: line 485: local: `&lt;a href=&quot;https://downloads.hpdd.intel.com/public/kernels/rhel7/old&amp;#39;:&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://downloads.hpdd.intel.com/public/kernels/rhel7/old&apos;:&lt;/a&gt; not a valid identifier&lt;br/&gt;
Downloading &lt;a href=&quot;http://vault.centos.org/centos/7/updates/Source/SPackages//kernel-3.10.0-862.2.3.el7.src.rpm&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://vault.centos.org/centos/7/updates/Source/SPackages//kernel-3.10.0-862.2.3.el7.src.rpm&lt;/a&gt;...&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This is caused by an extra space after &quot;local location=&quot;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
